            <p class="eyebrow">Service overview</p>
            <h2>What hydro jetting actually solves</h2>
            <p>Commercial drain lines fail differently than residential ones. Grease load is higher, run time is longer, and the cost of downtime is real. Hydro jetting cleans the inside of the pipe back to a working diameter so the line behaves the way the design intended.</p><p>Honest Drain matches nozzle and pressure to the line: chain knockers for cast iron with scale, flushing nozzles for grease lines, and root cutters for clay sewers. After-hours scheduling keeps the work out of operating hours.</p>
            <p class="link-row"><a class="text-link" href="../../contact.html">Book a service visit</a></p>
